{"tid":1590193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新文宣運動］中學生快入","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:29:36.000Z","uid":134294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0bc87fa53c1c8d701b6117bf635e723581b25b","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"大家都知鄰國國慶將近<br />\n各中學多數都會舉行升旗禮<br />\n既然今日局長佢都話如果學校取消升旗禮會發出錯誤訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我地緊係要慶佢老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我地可以點做呢<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n當然係係佢升旗嗰陣大大聲唱我國國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n咁做就應該有兩個結果嘅<br />\n一係學校收到風取消升旗禮<br />\n咁大家都唔洗眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就照舉行 但俾學生嘅歌聲遮蓋<br />\n激到班腥港人後代同藍底老師死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要大家一齊唱 唔落單<br />\n啲老師根本捉唔到人 <br />\n唔洗成本又可以畀多啲人 甚至附近街坊認識呢首歌 你唔係唔做呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同你身邊嘅朋友宣傳呢個國慶活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=78d2621c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a600f031fe301224a67dc892d636bc37bc74586","tid":1590193,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"a9299ecdb8bf001b6997e02bbbdd78bac0609f37","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"e552873d6b63de6098329e5e3c09945ac7c5cf52","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"656c6e30a02c210922195834aaef9524cbdcd1cb","tid":1590193,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c0fa14a344e9674645604a79cf57b39b50d6f934","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eb18286fea65368cfe177f551c42ab185368966","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5a815912cd7953d56012b584e0b1d57103886b4","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e19c625ee9b33c47d28079e9af6d5270f8397d5","tid":1590193,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:19:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd1b3c781f7af86c96d17b97c65429eb77ec6217","tid":1590193,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"Push推Pish<br />\n追求公平、自由、民主、公義、人權從來都唔易<br />\n漫長的道路上需要你支持我，我扶持你<br />\n儘管有時惘然若失，我們也要自信起來往前邁步<br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力捍衛同守護<br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，迎接未來<br />\n<br />\n短期目標：提升港人身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做<br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生，27個鄉X)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營，各有各做<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播公平民主思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull